1. Create an "VkApplicationInfo"
2. Create an "VkInstanceCreateInfo"
3. Create an "VkInstance"

4. Get amount of physical devices 
5. Create an "VkDeviceQueueCreateInfo"
6. Create an "VkDeviceCreateInfo"
7. Create an "VkDevice"
8. Set "VK_LAYER_LUNARG_standard_validation" layer
9. Create a "VkQueue"

10. Create a "VkSwapchainKHR"
11. Create a "VkImageView"

END: destroy the device and instance in reverse order of creation